# dashtrash

![Logo](https://via.placeholder.com/150)

**dashtrash** is a real-time terminal-based dashboard tool designed for developers, sysadmins, and DevOps engineers who want full monitoring capabilities with none of the SaaS baggage.

Banner Text: DashTrash
